#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H11_N1"
msgid ""
"白骨死体がある。\n"
"死後かなりの時間が\n"
"経過しているようだ。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"死体は、すぐとなりの\n"
"もうひとつの白骨死体と\n"
"抱き合っているように見える。"
msgstr ""
"There's a skeleton.\n"
"Looks like it's been\n"
"some time since it died.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"It looks like\n"
"it's hugging\n"
"with another skeleton."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H11_N2_MSG1"
msgid ""
"白骨死体がある。\n"
"死後かなりの時間が\n"
"経過しているようだ。"
msgstr ""
"There's a skeleton.\n"
"Looks like it's been\n"
"some time since it died."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H11_N2_SEL1"
msgid "死体を調べる"
msgstr "Check it out"

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H11_N2_SEL2"
msgid "ほっておく"
msgstr "Ignore it"

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_N4_MSG2"
msgid ""
"明るい色の、かつては\n"
"アロハシャツだったらしいぼろ布が、\n"
"骨にからみついている‥‥。"
msgstr ""
"Worn down silk, which might've\n"
"been a tropical shirt,\n"
"is entagled with the bones..."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_N4_MSG3"
msgid ""
"骨の下から、グリップに\n"
"象牙細工のほどこされた\n"
"ピストルを見つけた！{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"$npは、\n"
"$ni068を\n"
"手にいれた！"
msgstr ""
"You found a pistol\n"
"with an ivory grip\n"
"beneath the bones!{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"$np got the $ni068!"

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_DIARY"
msgid ""
"$npは\n"
"骨になった男の日記の\n"
"ページをめくった。"
msgstr ""
"$np\n"
"flipped through the pages\n"
"of the dead man's diary"

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_DIARY_P1"
msgid ""
"×月△日{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"＜$nn308＞とかいうアレが\n"
"始まって以来、このあたりも\n"
"異様に冷えこむようになった。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"どす黒く曇ったままの空からは\n"
"どす黒い雨ばかり降ってくる。\n"
"これが「核の冬」ってヤツか。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"死んだ魚が山のように\n"
"海岸にうちあげられていた。\n"
"とりあえず、冷凍しておく。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"魚は好きじゃないが、\n"
"貴重な食糧だ。\n"
"文句は言えん。"
msgstr ""
"Ever since that Great Destruction \n"
"has begun, this area has\n"
"become very cold.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"The skies are covered\n"
"in black clouds\n"
"and only black rain falls down.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"Is this a \"nuclear winter\"?{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"Lots of dead fishes wash up\n"
"in the beach\n"
"so I'll freeze them.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"Not fond of fishes\n"
"but they're food so...\n"
"Can't complain."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_DIARY_P2"
msgid ""
"×月×日{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"‥‥向こうの部屋の\n"
"若いカップルは\n"
"心中していた。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"せっかく生きのびたのに\n"
"自殺するとは‥‥\n"
"バカなヤツらだ。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"まぁ、おかげで、\n"
"残り少なくなった食いものが\n"
"多少は長くもつだろう。"
msgstr ""
"...The young couple\n"
"of the other room\n"
"did a lovers' suicide.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"You'd managed to survive\n"
"and yet you choose to die...\n"
"What fools.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"Oh well. As a result\n"
"the few fishes that were left\n"
"will last longer now. "

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_DIARY_P3"
msgid ""
"○月□日{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"目が覚めてみると、\n"
"妻の姿が消えていた。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"「あたしもう耐えれない‥‥\n"
"　先に行くわね」\n"
"という書きおきを残して。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"ひとりで水に入って\n"
"自殺したらしい‥‥。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"これでまた、\n"
"残り少ない食糧が\n"
"長くもつことになったぜ。"
msgstr ""
"When I woke up,\n"
"my wife was gone.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"She left a note...\n"
"“I can't bear this anymore...\n"
"I'll be going now.”{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"It'd seem she \n"
"went into the sea alone\n"
"and suicided...{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"And thus\n"
"the few food left\n"
"will last longer. "

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_DIARY_P4"
msgid ""
"○月×日{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"ヒマつぶしにあちこち\n"
"歩き回って、いろいろなものを\n"
"集めてきた‥‥。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"だがどうやらそれも\n"
"もう\n"
"ムリらしい‥‥。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"冷凍した魚を食って\n"
"生きのびてきたが‥‥\n"
"体調がいよいよ悪くなってきた。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"昔はまるで天国みたいな、\n"
"最高のビーチだったのになぁ。\n"
"いまは、地獄だ。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"待たせたな、おまえ。\n"
"オレも今から行くよ‥‥。{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"もし、あの世で、\n"
"もう一度会えたなら‥‥\n"
"愛してると言ってくれ。"
msgstr ""
"I walked around\n"
"and picked up stuff\n"
"to kill the boredom...{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"But looks like\n"
"I'll no longer\n"
"be able to do so...{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"I've survived\n"
"by eating the frozen fish but...\n"
"My health is failing me.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"This used to be a great beach\n"
"which felt like a paradise but...\n"
"Now it's Hell itself.{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"Kept you waiting, dear.\n"
"I'll be going there, too...{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"If I get to\n"
"meet you in the afterlife...\n"
"Tell me you love me."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_FAKE_END_MSG1"
msgid ""
"こうして、\n"
"$nn008と$npは\n"
"自由で、幸福な\n"
"人生をおくった。"
msgstr ""
"And so, Cola and $np\n"
"lived together,\n"
"freely and happily."

#. Text size: 58 characters x 3 lines.{END TEXTBOX}\n is \0
msgctxt "// H17_FAKE_END_MSG2"
msgid ""
"それは愛に満ちた\n"
"素晴らしい日々だったが、\n"
"平凡で退屈な\n"
"人生でもあった‥‥。\n"
"　　　　　　　　　　　（つづく）"
msgstr ""
"They were\n"
"wonderful days\n"
"filled with love,{END TEXTBOX}\n"
"but also\n"
"ordinary and boring...\n"
"　　　　　　　　(To Be Continued)"

